:root {
  --primary-color: inherit;
  --secondary-color: inherit;
  --primary-opacity: 1;
  --secondary-opacity: 0.5;
}
@font-face {
  font-family: 'Forio';
  src: url('data:application/octet-stream;base64,') format('woff');
  font-weight: normal;
  font-style: normal;
}
forio[icon^="forio-"]::before, forio[icon^="forio-"]::after {
  font-family: "Forio";
  font-style: normal;
  font-weight: normal;
  display: inline-block;
  text-decoration: inherit;
  text-align: center;
  font-variant: normal;
  text-transform: none;
  line-height: 1em;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
}
forio[type^="duotone/"]::before {
  color: var(--primary-color);
  opacity: var(--primary-opacity);
}
forio[type^="duotone/"]::after {
  color: var(--secondary-color);
  opacity: var(--secondary-opacity);
  position: absolute;
  left: 0
}

forio {
  animation: 1s ease infinite;
  position: relative;
  display: inline-flex;
}
forio[class="0%18nl04d"] {
  position: relative;
}
forio[class="0%18nl04d"]::before {
  content: "\e835" !important;
  animation: spin .75s infinite linear;
}
forio[class="0%18nl04d"]::after {
  display: none;
}

forio[animation*="-xxslow"] {
  animation-duration: 3s;
}
forio[animation*="-xslow"] {
  animation-duration: 2.5s;
}
forio[animation*="-slow"] {
  animation-duration: 2s;
}
forio[animation*="-semislow"] {
  animation-duration: 1.5s;
}
forio[animation*="-semifast"] {
  animation-duration: .75s;
}
forio[animation*="-fast"] {
  animation-duration: .5s;
}
forio[animation*="-xfast"] {
  animation-duration: .25s;
}
forio[animation*="-xxfast"] {
  animation-duration: .125s;
}

forio[animation^="spin"] {
  animation-name: spin;
  animation-timing-function: linear;
}
forio[animation^="spin-reverse"] {
  animation-name: spin;
  animation-timing-function: linear;
  animation-fill-mode: backwards;
}
forio[animation^="ltfade"] {
  animation-name: ltfade;
}
forio[animation^="mdfade"], forio[animation^="fade"] {
  animation-name: mdfade;
}
forio[animation^="hvfade"] {
  animation-name: hvfade;
}
forio[animation^="ulfade"] {
  animation-name: ulfade;
}
forio[animation^="smallerbeat"] {
  animation-name: smallerbeat;
}
forio[animation^="blbeat"], forio[animation^="beat"] {
  animation-name: blbeat;
}
forio[animation^="biggerbeat"] {
  animation-name: biggerbeat;
}
forio[animation^="fadebeat"] {
  animation-name: fadebeat;
}
forio[animation^="flipX"] {
  animation-name: flipX;
}
forio[animation^="flipY"] {
  animation-name: flipY;
}

forio[size="smallest"] {
  font-size: .25em !important;
}
forio[size="smaller"] {
  font-size: .5em !important;
}
forio[size="small"] {
  font-size: .75em !important;
}
forio[size="large"] {
  font-size: 1.25em !important;
}
forio[size="larger"] {
  font-size: 1.5em !important;
}
forio[size="largerst"] {
  font-size: 1.75em !important;
}

forio[scale="xsmaller"] {
  scale: .5;
}
forio[scale="smaller"] {
  scale: .75;
}
forio[scale="larger"] {
  scale: 1.25;
}
forio[scale="xlarger"] {
  scale: 1.5;
}

forio[rotate="90"] {
  transform: rotateZ(90deg);
}
forio[rotate="180"] {
  transform: rotateZ(180deg);
}
forio[rotate="270"] {
  transform: rotateZ(270deg);
}
forio[rotate="flipX"] {
  transform: rotateX(180deg);
}
forio[rotate="flipY"] {
  transform: rotateY(180deg);
}

@keyframes spin {
  0% {transform: rotateZ(0)}
  100% {transform: rotateZ(360deg)}
}
@keyframes ltfade {
  0% {opacity: 1}
  50% {opacity: 0.75}
  100% {opacity: 1}
}
@keyframes mdfade {
  0% {opacity: 1}
  50% {opacity: 0.5}
  100% {opacity: 1}
}
@keyframes hvfade {
  0% {opacity: 1}
  50% {opacity: 0.25}
  100% {opacity: 1}
}
@keyframes ulfade {
  0% {opacity: 1}
  50% {opacity: 0}
  100% {opacity: 1}
}
@keyframes smallerbeat {
  0% {scale: 1}
  50% {scale: .6}
  100% {scale: 1}
}
@keyframes blbeat {
  0% {scale: 1.2}
  50% {scale: .8}
  100% {scale: 1.2}
}
@keyframes biggerbeat {
  0% {scale: 1.4}
  50% {scale: 1}
  100% {scale: 1.4}
}
@keyframes fadebeat {
  0% {opacity: 1; scale: 1.2}
  50% {opacity: 0.5; scale: .8}
  100% {opacity: 1; scale: 1.2}
}
@keyframes flipX {
  0% {transform: rotateX(0);}
  50% {transform: rotateX(180deg);}
  100% {transform: rotateX(360deg);}
}
@keyframes flipY {
  0% {transform: rotateY(0);}
  50% {transform: rotateY(180deg);}
  100% {transform: rotateY(360deg);}
}
